er \u003cckerschb@christophkerschbaumer.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1497205: Apply Meta CSP to about:restartrequired.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D36574", "files": ["browser/base/content/aboutRestartRequired.js", "browser/base/content/aboutRestartRequired.xhtml", "modules/libpref/init/all.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e73d78cdb0c0ab9c168c98e4c859075ae4736b65", "parents": ["997f6179442e6a146b24e176bb7057aa10669a29"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Marco Bonardo \u003cmbonardo@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1547669 - Improve the TopSites WebExtension API with further options. r=mixedpuppy,Mardak,adw\n\nAdds includePinned and includeSearchShortcuts options to the topSites API, so\nthat it's possible to get a list of results like it's shown on the newtab page.\nBoth options default to false, so that the existing behavior is preserved.\nThe API gets disabled on Android; this API always depended on APIs not well\nsupported there, and the test is disabled on Android, so it was untested.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D36467", "files": ["toolkit/components/extensions/jar.mn", "toolkit/components/extensions/parent/ext-topSites.js", "toolkit/components/extensions/schemas/jar.mn", "toolkit/components/extensions/schemas/top_sites.json", "toolkit/components/extensions/test/xpcshell/test_ext_topSites.js", "toolkit/components/places/Bookmarks.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "99f94dd8c8f1f0ca13196051cf608b420b5df731", "parents": ["e73d78cdb0c0ab9c168c98e4c859075ae4736b65"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Arpit Bharti \u003carpitbharti73@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1083971 - Add an option to output a binary file for the PSL data r=leplatrem,erahm\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D34364", "files": ["netwerk/dns/prepare_tlds.py", "xpcom/ds/tools/make_dafsa.py"], "git_node": nu