d54344797dddbc7dfc49de2b1f6"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Cosmin Sabou \u003ccsabou@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Merge mozilla-central to autoland.", "files": [], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null, null], "node": "7eff60789f10b2766615d486b8e9c1568b7efcbd", "parents": ["0ab7f6c67d4be16e78cdac5b729729646a3375e5", "5f0961efaa1c01e5b4bc449ee5d58260393291ef"], "tags": []}, {"author": "thomasmo \u003cthomasmo@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1562777 - Refactor ShMem code from VR classes into separate class r=kip\n\nThis change brings the related ShMem code from VRManager and VRService into a\nnew class, VRShMem. This is to support future work where this ShMem will be used\nfor other efforts. Having this code in the same class will enable it to be more\neasily shared in these efforts.\nUntil the new class replaces the code in VRManager and VRService, it can be\nexercised and validated with two instances of vrtesthost, with the -testmgr and\n-testsvc parameters.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D36649", "files": ["gfx/vr/VRShMem.cpp", "gfx/vr/VRShMem.h", "gfx/vr/external_api/moz_external_vr.h", "gfx/vr/gfxVRMutex.h", "gfx/vr/moz.build", "gfx/vr/vrhost/moz.build", "gfx/vr/vrhost/testhost/testhost.cpp", "gfx/vr/vrhost/vrhost.cpp", "gfx/vr/vrhost/vrhost.def"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3fe0f2c3a8754730c5335862f40f84bdea58a081", "parents": ["7eff60789f10b2766615d486b8e9c1568b7efcbd"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andrea Marchesini \u003camarchesini@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1563032 - BodyStream must check the return value of BodyStreamHolder::GetReadableStreamBody(), r=smaug\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D36717", "files": ["dom/base/BodyStream.cpp", "dom/base/BodyStream.h", "dom/fetch/Fetch.h", "dom/file/Blob.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "45d9572f4a3705dfa346e35aa973438f2374ed98", "parents": ["3fe0f2c3a8754730c5335862f40f84bdea58a081"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Edwin Gao \u003cegao@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1562083 - explicitly insert sys.path to env for use in subprocess for python3 mozprocess unit tests r=jmaher\n\nChanges:\n- for macosx1014, in the tests where `subprocess` is called and the process relies on `six` being present, ensure that `six` is available in the PYTHONPATH by explicitly inserting the contents of `sys.path` to the modified environment variable dict\n- change how the command line call to run the suite is being built in `taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/job/mach.py`\n- migrate source-tests from macosx1010 to macosx1014\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D36681", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/source-test/python.yml", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/job/mach.py", "testing/mozbase/mozprocess/tests/test_kill.py", "testing/mozbase/mozprocess/tests/test_misc.py", "testing/mozbase/mozprocess/tests/test_wait.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "da3af6a077fc1273e1062f558af635a2cef642f4", "parents": ["45d9572f4a3705dfa346e35aa973438f2374ed98"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Cosmin Sabou \u003ccsabou@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out changeset da3af6a077fc (bug 1562083) for busting gecko decision task. CLOSED TREE", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/source-test/python.yml", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/job/mach.py", "testing/mozbase/mozprocess/tests/test_kill.py", "testing/mozbase/mozprocess/tests/test_misc.py", "testing/mozbase/mozprocess/tests/test_wait.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "be232271fcde16cffc84ef2f24a8e849302c5991", "parents": ["da3af6a077fc1273e1062f558af635a2cef642f4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Dana Keeler \u003cdkeeler@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "bug 1553550 - removing expiring intermediate preloading telemetry r=jcj\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D36