la@hocat.ca\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1562628: Run the periodic file update cron job on ESR68; r=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D36787", "files": [".cron.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0af1dfabc22b28f26d56440fe04c91fca5461d40", "parents": ["6ed76105f2b33d10bed605e523cd786c12adfb06"], "tags": []}, {"author": "kriswright \u003ckwright@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "bug 1562309 - add protected data checks to check for context-local thread data r=jonco\n\nAdds CheckContextLocal protected data checks and a data type to check a JSContext against the TlsContext of the thread. Objects must specify the JSContext in which they are created in to check against.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D36518", "files": ["js/src/threading/ProtectedData.cpp", "js/src/threading/ProtectedData.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "636ffcf7e25184078c20c6323d8e42bf4a68b7d4", "parents": ["0af1dfabc22b28f26d56440fe04c91fca5461d40"], "tags": []}, {"author": "kriswright \u003ckwright@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "bug 1562309 - 2. Convert ThreadData in JSContext to ContextData r=jonco\n\nConvert ThreadData to ContextData in JSContext. Removed some old GCHelperState variables that are no longer being used. Removed NativeStackQuota, which is never read. Renamed SetNativeStackQuotaAndLimit to SetNativeStackLimit, as it is never setting a NativeStackQuota.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D36533", "files": ["js/src/jsapi.cpp", "js/src/vm/JSContext.cpp", "js/src/vm/JSContext.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "dc1ad84da67e3a3e51326c59cbe9bffdca6e0e1e", "parents": ["636ffcf7e25184078c20c6323d8e42bf4a68b7d4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Julian Descottes \u003cjdescottes@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1562583 - Add license headers in devtools/shared/protocol fi