"desc": "Backed out changeset b4f0e8b4b6fa (bug 1559365) for causing browser-chrome failures in AboutLoginsParent.jsm", "files": ["browser/components/BrowserGlue.jsm", "browser/components/aboutlogins/AboutLoginsChild.jsm", "browser/components/aboutlogins/AboutLoginsParent.jsm", "browser/components/aboutlogins/content/aboutLogins.js", "browser/components/aboutlogins/content/components/login-list-item.css", "browser/components/aboutlogins/content/components/login-list.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "91d8f385c5e5ec15c5cdb1d6c24b582fe1862acc", "parents": ["921eab31ab8eaa9c381d5c44b65fc2045c97845a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "alwu \u003calwu@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1541452 - update cue display when window is resized. r=heycam\n\nWhen window is resized, the cue would usually be zoomed in or out automatically with the video and keep its relative position to video.\n\nHowever, if video is being applied the explicit percentage value on its 'width' or 'height', we have to recompute cue's position in this situation, because the width or height of the video would be scaled again after applied the first size scaled which is caused by resizing.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D36138", "files": ["dom/html/TextTrackManager.cpp", "layout/generic/nsVideoFrame.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "16485dcacef6087da868ac4fef2ad829850db195", "parents": ["91d8f385c5e5ec15c5cdb1d6c24b582fe1862acc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan-Ivar Bruaroey \u003cjib@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1528031 - Require [SecureContext] for navigator.mediaDevices & navigator.mozGetUserMedia(). r=pehrsons,smaug\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D33836", "files": ["modules/libpref/init/StaticPrefList.h", "testing/web-platform/meta/mediacapture-record/__dir__.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/mediacapture-streams/__dir__.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6d317cd3124aafefc18ffd0ac2056bfe76a119bb", "parents": ["16485dcacef6087da868ac4fef2ad829850db195"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan-Ivar Bruaroey \u003cjib@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1528031 - Update tests to work with [SecureContext] navigator.mediaDevices. r=pehrsons,smaug\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D35970", "files": ["dom/media/test/crashtests/crashtests.list", "dom/media/tests/crashtests/crashtests.list", "dom/media/tests/mochitest/test_getUserMedia_permission.html", "dom/media/tests/mochitest/test_peerConnection_basicAudioNATRelay.html", "dom/media/tests/mochitest/test_peerConnection_basicAudioNATRelayTCP.html", "dom/media/tests/mochitest/test_peerConnection_basicAudioNATRelayTLS.html", "dom/media/tests/mochitest/test_peerConnection_basicAudioNATSrflx.html", "dom/media/tests/mochitest/test_peerConnection_stats_relayProtocol.html", "dom/tests/mochitest/general/test_interfaces.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "948869e38bce72ae635e1ab629ab42ce0af444cc", "parents": ["6d317cd3124aafefc18ffd0ac2056bfe76a119bb"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Olli Pettay \u003cOlli.Pettay@helsinki.fi\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1559523 - Fix a crash in Thunderbird, [@ mozilla::dom::Document::EndLoad]. r=kaie", "files": ["dom/base/Document.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2514efbfbb783ebbdbf6c84751e2c464a8d65d83", "parents": ["c7e91f614eb78c4447a623f1c88a66421113ab07"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mihai Alexandru Michis \u003cmalexandru@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Merge inbound to mozilla-central. a=merge", "files": [], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null, null], "node": "2b1bee2c77347e39b4a6f0023cf1a7dabc4db607", "parents": ["ea6af5ad89e2040f1bfe28f49adcf14f6e65f4d5", "2514efbfbb783ebbdbf6c84751e2c464a8d65d83"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mihai Alexandru Michis \u003cmalexandru@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Merge mozilla-central to autoland.  a=merge CLOSED TREE", "files": [], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null, null], "node": "49b6eb1732c979a1129e7237ef75d4cb967e2489", "parents": ["948869e38bce72ae635e1ab629ab42ce0af444cc", "2b1bee2c77347e39b4a6f0023cf1a7dabc4db607"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Kagami Sascha Rosylight \u003csaschanaz@outlook.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 770286: Prevent git LF-to-CRLF autoconversion r=glandium\n\nCurrently git for Windows converts LF to CRLF by default, so this change prevents that to match the mercurial behavior.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D32001", "files": [".gitattributes"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "4762f5a28a7287d48d3f6c90fe7a9e7b2b8c0c10", "parents": ["49b6eb1732c979a1129e7237ef75d4cb967e2489"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jim Blandy \u003cjimb@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1560754: Remove DebuggeeFrameGeneratorScript. r=jorendorff\n\nStop inserting DebuggeeFrameGeneratorScript keys in the cross-compartment\nwrapper table for the edges from Debugger.Frames for generator / async calls to\nthe generators' scripts. The wrappers are unnecessary, and since they're not\nunique when multiple Debugger.Frames refer to different calls of the same\ngenerator, we can't easily tell when to remove them.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D35617", "files": ["js/src/jit-test/tests/debug/bug1557343-2.js", "js/src/vm/Compartment.h", "js/src/vm/Debugger.cpp", "js/src/vm/Debugger.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1dd4e16a1a9633c661abd2da224d1046259513e0", "parents": ["4762f5a28a7287d48d3f6c90fe7a9e7b2b8c0c10"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Kagami Sascha Rosylight \u003csaschanaz@outlook.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1563504: Implement DOMPoint matrixTransform() r=bzbarsky\n\nTry: https://treeherder.mozilla.org/#/jobs?repo=try&revision=619248c60ce6a3f432c13abe7e7bc5bbf03c4184 (7 un