h local rect TypedRect(1561.0\u00d71968.0 at (-300.0,-300.0))\n        clip Rectangle(3840.0\u00d71874.0, Clip) at (0.0,0.0) in space SpatialNodeIndex(1)\n        flags (empty), resulted in Partial\n        clip Rectangle(3840.0\u00d71874.0, Clip) at (0.0,0.0) in space SpatialNodeIndex(2)\n        flags (empty), resulted in Partial\n```\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D37137", "files": ["gfx/wr/webrender/src/clip.rs", "gfx/wr/webrender/src/prim_store/mod.rs"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f1b593ede263787c8710ef5f211195e5c8dda02f", "parents": ["ec9aff5bd85633c81ebf964f54808f33ee6cf379"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ciure Andrei \u003caciure@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out changeset fe8c2426d9d3 (bug 1514474) for causing beta simulation failures CLOSED TREE", "files": ["dom/security/featurepolicy/FeaturePolicy.cpp", "dom/security/featurepolicy/FeaturePolicy.h", "dom/security/featurepolicy/test/mochitest/mochitest.ini", "dom/security/featurepolicy/test/mochitest/test_featureList.html", "dom/webidl/FeaturePolicy.webidl"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "fddbb046b7c1ac4ccf47305241716348270d76dc", "parents": ["f1b593ede263787c8710ef5f211195e5c8dda02f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreea Pavel \u003capavel@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out changeset f1b593ede263 (bug 1563993) for wrench bustages on a CLOSED TREE", "files": ["gfx/wr/webrender/src/clip.rs", "gfx/wr/webrender/src/prim_store/mod.rs"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "fec2c81434b4daecc226168a761fbd0b8229d8b7", "parents": ["fddbb046b7c1ac4ccf47305241716348270d76dc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jared Wein \u003cjwein@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1562255 - Move 'Create new login' button to the bottom of the login list. r=MattN,fluent-reviewers,flod\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D37133", "files": ["browser/component