, the top sites API returns search results with aliases but not names. We should let extensions specify engine URLs and aliases, and we can use them to look up the engine name.\n\nThe UrlbarResult.jsm change is unrelated but fixes a minor annoyance I found while working on the top-sites extension. My background script returns results with `isKeywordOffer: true`, but that causes an error in `UrlbarResult.payloadAndSimpleHighlights` because it converts string values to arrays and then expects non-string values to be arrays. Instead, it should be converting non-array values to arrays.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D39800", "files": ["browser/components/extensions/test/xpcshell/test_ext_urlbar.js", "browser/components/urlbar/UrlbarProviderExtension.jsm", "browser/components/urlbar/UrlbarResult.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "210540f1db7455a3941cc9b6f5b6baaa71ef54bc", "parents": ["5163a1983a95573f1d0b10cfd875c16f4249c099"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreea Pavel \u003capavel@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1565273 - Right click Address bar does not select whole url r=mak a=RyanVM", "files": ["browser/components/urlbar/UrlbarInput.jsm", "browser/components/urlbar/tests/browser/browser.ini", "browser/components/urlbar/tests/browser/browser_urlbar_selection.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "209780edbdf9b660eb86fc50dea6041b3a4f977f", "parents": ["210540f1db7455a3941cc9b6f5b6baaa71ef54bc"], "tags": []}], "date": 1564860042, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "apavel@mozilla.com"}, "11710": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\ndsb -\u003e 8cbc2a851bef\neo -\u003e 41c4ecb48013\nfr -\u003e e35a00ebfb99\nhsb -\u003e ac23c02b8bef\nit -\u003e 491f03fc6d6b", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "858ea1f8449e880fbe0826377e13fec117908bac", "parents": ["209780edbdf9b660eb86fc50dea6041b3a4f977f"], "tags": []}], "date": 1564862431, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "11711": {"changesets": [{"author": "Daniel Varga \u003cdvarga@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out changeset 209780edbdf9 (bug 1565273) for browser-chrome failures at browser/components/urlbar/tests/browser/browser_urlbar_selection.js a=backout", "files": ["browser/components/urlbar/UrlbarInput.jsm", "browser/components/urlbar/tests/browser/browser.ini", "browser/components/urlbar/tests/browser/browser_urlbar_selection.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1270a56d8bb7f6df12008e24b0e56d3b7cf9a160", "parents": ["858ea1f8449e880fbe0826377e13fec117908bac"], "tags": []}], "date": 1564866284, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "dvarga@mozilla.com"}, "11712": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nen-CA -\u003e 808b1ed141c0\neo -\u003e 58d0f3a174f9\nes-CL -\u003e 29fde7846616\nit -\u003e b93279aa510b\nsv-SE -\u003e 4481a6e30d9a\nth -\u003e 7cc730af536f\nvi -\u003e c931fcb907be", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8e8729d81f57e6ac517240bcc504bee085a85f97", "parents": ["1270a56d8bb7f6df12008e24b0e56d3b7cf9a160"], "tags": []}, {"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nen-CA -\u003e 808b1ed141c0\neo -\u003e 58d0f3a174f9\nes-CL -\u003e 29fde7846616\nia -\u003e e69c061e90a5\nit -\u003e b93279aa510b\nsv-SE -\u003e 4481a6e30d9a\nth -\u003e 7cc730af536f\nvi -\u003e c931fcb907be", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node"